---
import Mainlayout from "../layouts/mainlayout.astro";
---
<Mainlayout>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden w-full h-[12rem] md:h-[20rem] bg-cover bg-center bg-[url('/about-banner-bg.jpg')]">
        <div class="p-6 max-w-6xl">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-center text-white">Empower Charities, Amplify Impact</h1>
            <p class="text-white text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto py-2">My Sadaqah Online: The leading Donation Fulfillment Platform platform revolutionizing Sadaqah and Qurbani services for charities, ensuring delivery within 48 hours.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row p-12 bg-gray-50 space-y-6 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-6">
        <div class="p-6 rounded-lg w-full md:w-1/3">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Our Vision & Principles</h2>
            <div class="mb-4">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-black">Empowering Charities with Technology</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">We harness the transformative power of technology to revolutionize how charities facilitate Sadaqah and Qurbani, creating a seamless bridge between donors' intentions and impactful actions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-4">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-black">Pioneering Solutions</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Our innovative Donation Fulfillment Platform platform prioritizes both charity operations and donor experiences, ensuring precision and maximum benefit delivery within 48 hours.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-4">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-black">Transparency and Security</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">We provide tools for complete transparency in service delivery while ensuring the utmost security of all data. We never sell or trade personal information.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden md:block md:w-px bg-gray-300"></div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-lg w-full md:w-2/3">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
            <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-black mb-2">"The Believer's Shade On The Day Of Resurrection Will Be His Sadaqah" (Hadith Tirmidhi)</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">At My Sadaqah Online, we understand that Sadaqah and Qurbani are powerful means of creating positive change and multiplying rewards. Their impact is greatest when executed swiftly, addressing urgent needs.</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">In our fast-paced world, charities often struggle with timely Sadaqah and Qurbani delivery. Our platform ensures charities can complete these services within 48 hours, maximizing the effectiveness of donors' generosity.</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Our mission is to make Sadaqah and Qurbani services seamless and timely for charities. We provide a robust Donation Fulfillment Platform platform to help charitable organizations fulfill their commitments efficiently, ensuring donations have the most significant impact at crucial times.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="p-12 bg-white">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 text-center">Our Services</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-black mb-2">Sadaqah & Qurbani Management</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Comprehensive systems for charities to process, track, and deliver Sadaqah donations and Qurbani orders efficiently.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-black mb-2">Proof of Delivery</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Automated systems to capture and share evidence of completed Sadaqah and Qurbani with donors, enhancing transparency.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-black mb-2">Integration Solutions</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Custom API integrations to seamlessly connect our platform with charities' existing websites and systems.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="p-12 bg-gray-50">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 text-center">Join Us in Revolutionizing Charitable Giving</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-6">My Sadaqah Online isn't just a platform; it's a movement towards more efficient, transparent, and impactful charitable giving. We invite charities to join us in this mission, leveraging our technology to amplify their impact.</p>
        <div class="text-center">
            <a href="#" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white py-2 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition duration-300">Register Your Charity</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</Mainlayout>